Malawi’s Tourism Agency Against Oil Drilling on Lake, Times Says

-- B y   F r a n k   J o m o
-- 
2011-10-06T08:43:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-06/malawi-s-tourism-agency-against-oil-drilling-on-lake-times-says.html
Malawi’s Tourism Ministry said
awarding U.K.-based Surestream Petroleum Ltd. a license to
explore for oil on Lake Malawi could harm aquatic life, the
Daily Times reported, citing Director of Tourism Isaac Katopola.  To contact the reporter on this story:
